    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a good-condition example that is clean, well-kept, and enjoyable to drive, while still showing the light signs of normal use you would expect from a car of this age. The paint, trim, and interior present nicely overall, though a close look will reveal some minor cosmetic wear and small imperfections rather than a show-level finish. It appears to have been cared for and remains a very respectable driver with solid overall presentation. Buyers should expect a car that looks good, feels usable and maintained, and would be a strong choice for someone who wants a nice example to enjoy without paying mint-condition money.",
      "price": 32900.0,
