    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, honest transportation with plenty of potential. This vehicle offers a practical entry point for a buyer looking for dependable basic mobility, a project opportunity, or a low-cost second car. Priced to reflect its age and condition while still delivering real value, it stands out as a straightforward purchase for someone who wants maximum utility without a big investment.",
