      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s not winning any beauty contests, but it starts, runs, and can still be a handy budget set of wheels for someone who needs basic transport. It\u2019s got the usual age and wear you\u2019d expect and would suit a buyer who doesn\u2019t mind a bit of TLC. If you\u2019re after something cheap, straightforward, and full of potential as a runabout or project, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Dependable project or budget daily with solid fundamentals and plenty of upside. Starts, runs, and moves, with a durable powertrain layout and straightforward mechanicals that make it a practical candidate for someone who wants affordable transportation or a hands-on fixer-upper. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but it offers good parts value, usable drivability, and room to improve without a huge buy-in. Priced to sell for the next owner who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
