      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that feels like it has stories left to tell. It\u2019s a budget-friendly entry for someone who appreciates a vehicle with personality, whether you\u2019re looking for a hands-on project, a practical spare, or something with unmistakable presence in the driveway. There\u2019s real potential here for the next owner with vision: a chance to shape it into exactly what you want while starting from a price point that leaves room for that journey. If you like your cars with grit, charm, and opportunity, this one delivers all three.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a straightforward choice for anyone seeking affordable transportation without unnecessary frills. It shows its age, but it remains a practical option for commuting, errands, or as a starter vehicle. Offered with honest value in mind, this is a chance to get into a car at a very accessible price point.",
