    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it starts, runs, and gives you a practical set of wheels at a very approachable price. Great for a handy owner, a backup vehicle, or someone looking for an inexpensive project. If you want honest value and room to make it your own, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
